gomodel:SYNGO_1581  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" , "Rationale: A new antibody specific for the C-terminus of mGluR7 was raised and shown to react to mGluR7. EM of rat brain sections showed that mGluR7 was presynaptically localized to asymmetric synapses, though there were a few instances of postnsynaptic localization.\n\n20/11/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Sprague-Dawley, Materials & Methods" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5648-066X" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2533-9548" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4022-8707" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7480-0826" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1212-5623" ;
